br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家記得我地要壯大黃色圈, 而唔係將黃色圈門檻愈set愈高, <br />\n要黃, 唔一定要深黃, 但要贏, 就一定要拉攏更多人去變黃.</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05db3ec863ebfd7f12797c0c9b704f2d078b1a23","tid":1957034,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d68e4aa79cba0af1f7e32cd1770856cbba9b78","tid":1957034,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"成個連登都係分化<br />\n無上好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c1fe004f1f0e9cd61ff47e1d9d29a1944da265","tid":1957034,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa2b15889702b60547f8d4f2ca115671e0e29ff","tid":1957034,"uid":314604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:26:28.000Z","msg":"有好多人冇連登account係度睇 不推文 提一提全部係blocked user會好啲"},{"pid":"1fa350d8714ea5fbfd4cfafbfcb2bad9044e52e8","tid":1957034,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"來來去去都係個幾招<br />\n同當年係高登分化本土派一樣"},{"pid":"3901a3e71be83f324347f8d1de858f0162b4c45b","tid":1957034,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"好多所謂批鬥都係佢地帶起先<br />\n然後話返你「兒登仔」"},{"pid":"4413be230864778716db74d1e6ba41d884923fea","tid":1957034,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"你以為真係咁多人比佢分化到<br />\n<br />\n其家都係班藍屍同狗係到扯貓尾"},{"pid":"36e7884fd7c237d3e778f117a4d37